{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji12","name":"毛泽东全集第12卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji12.pdf"],"article":{"title":"关于诗歌的指示","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"关于诗歌的指示"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1938年9月）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"诗歌要反映人民生活，要写抗日的现实斗争，才能完成诗歌的革命任务。因此，诗歌工作者要参加人民群众的生活。还有，诗歌要用接近群众的语言来写，群众才喜爱。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1938,"month":9}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":452,"page_end":452},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"指示"}]}]}